    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this car\u2014it\u2019s an absolute gem and looks just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken incredibly good care of it, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel. Everything is spotless, inside and out, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been pampered and is ready for a new home, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
